title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 §§ 80-5.2 - General requirements

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 §§ 80-5.2 - General requirements

State Regulations

The requirements set forth in Subpart 80-1 of this Part
shall be applicable, unless the subject matter or terms of such requirements
prescribe otherwise. Notes
